---

<section class = "h-screen snap-start flex flex-col justify-center">
    <div class = "mx-8 sm:mx-16 md:mx-24 max-w-2xl
        flex flex-col items-start justify-center
        ">
        <p class = "text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold ">
            I Build things to solve real-world problems.
        </p>
        <p class = "text-base 
            md:text-[clamp(0.9rem,2.5vw,1rem)]
            mt-8"> 
            I'm a software engineer from a non-traditional background 
            who builds practical applications to solve real-world problems,
            from "what's the lunch today?" to a chatbot that provide
            professional advice in specific domain.
        </p>
        <div class= "mt-12 h-16 overflow-visible">
            <a 
                href="#contact"
                class = "inline-block border p-4 rounded-sm text-base
                border-red-500 
                hover:-translate-y-1 hover:-translate-x-1
                border-b-1 border-r-1 border-l-1 border-t-1 
                hover:border-b-4 hover:border-r-4
                cursor-pointer transition"
                >
                Contact Me
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
